<div class="info-box">
    <p>
        This website is a simple Workout Tracker that helps users record their daily exercises.
        The user can add the name of the exercise, the number of reps or sets, and other details.
        All added exercises will appear in a small table on the same page.
        The goal of this website is to make it easier for people to keep track of their workouts.
    </p>
